title: 118: Biggest Week 2 Storylines
itunes:title: 118: Biggest Week 2 Storylines
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks take a look at the entire Week 2 slate through a scouting perspective and analyze the key matchup inside each game. Will Josh Norman travel this week against Dez Bryant? Can Rex Ryan get the Bills offense going against the Jets? The guys then dive into the huge weekend of college football.
